Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def

This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeActivityContainerDef Interface for all containers of activities.
IAeActivityCreateInstanceDef Interface to define an activity which has a createInstance attribute.
IAeBPELConstants Contains the list of BPEL Constants.
IAeCatchParentDef Interface for adding a catch or catchAll to a fault handler container.
IAeCompensateParentDef Tagging interface for container defs that can have compensate activities nested within them
IAeCompensationHandlerParentDef BPEL constructs that parent the 'compensationHandler' construct should implement this interface.
IAeConditionParentDef All constructs that can have a condition child should implement this interface.
IAeCorrelationSetsParentDef Parents of the 'correlationSets' construct should implement this interface.
IAeCorrelationsParentDef Any activity that can have a 'correlations' child must implement this interface.
IAeEventHandlersParentDef Defs that can be a parent of the 'eventHandlers' construct should implement this interface.
IAeExpressionDef Interface for all defs that can be expressions.
IAeFaultHandlersParentDef Bpel constructs that have a child called 'faultHandlers' should implement this interface.
IAeFCTHandlerDef Tagging interface for defs that model a fault, compensation, or termination handler.
IAeForUntilParentDef Defs that can have 'for' and 'until' children will implement this interface.
IAeFromParentDef Defs that can have a 'from' child will implement this interface.
IAeFromPartsParentDef Defs that can have a fromParts child construct will implement this interface.
IAeMessageExchangesParentDef Parents of 'messageExchanges' constructs must implement this interface.
IAeMultipleActivityContainerDef Interface for all containers of mutliple activities.
IAePartnerLinkParentDef Interface for the def and def, both of which can contain partner link references.
IAePartnerLinksParentDef Constructs that can be the parent of a 'partnerLinks' container def should implement this interface.
IAeQueryDef Interface for defs that have queries (like )
IAeSingleActivityContainerDef Interface for all containers of single activities.
IAeTerminationHandlerParentDef BPEL constructs that parent the 'terminationHandler' construct should implement this interface.
IAeToPartsParentDef Defs that can have a toParts child construct will implement this interface.
IAeUncrossableLinkBoundary Interface used to mark defs that links cannot cross.
IAeVariableParentDef interface for a def that defines a variable
IAeVariablesParentDef Bpel constructs that can have a 'variables' child must implement this interface.
 

Class Summary
AeActivityCreateInstanceBaseDef Base definition class for activities which is the createInstance attribute.
AeActivityDef Definition for bpel base activity definition.
AeActivityPartnerLinkBaseDef Definition for bpel partner link based activity
AeBaseContainer Base class for def objects that have a collection of other objects which need to be visited as a collection and/or individually.
AeBaseDef Base definition object for bpel definitions
AeBaseDefNamespaceContext A concrete implementation of a namespace context that uses a bpel def object as the namespace info source.
AeCatchAllDef Definition for bpel default fault handler activity.
AeCatchDef Definition for bpel fault handler element.
AeCompensationHandlerDef Models the 'compensationHandler' bpel construct.
AeCorrelationCombinations Maintains a collection of the different correlation set combinations that exists for a single partnerlink and operation.
AeCorrelationsDef Container class for correlations that are a part of receive, reply, invoke, and pick.
AeCorrelationSetDef Definition for bpel correlation set.
AeCorrelationSetsDef Container for correlationSets.
AeDocumentationDef A def implementation of the ws-bpel 2.0 <documentation> construct.
AeEventHandlersDef This is the container for event handlers for a scope.
AeExtensionActivityDef Models the 'extensionActivity' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeExtensionAttributeDef A simple class that holds the information about an extension attribute (namespace, qualified name, value).
AeExtensionDef Models the 'extension' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeExtensionsDef Models the 'extensions' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeFaultHandlersDef Container class for fault handlers (catch or catchAll) attached to a scope.
AeImportDef Definition of a ws-bpel 2.0 import.
AeMessageExchangeDef Models a WS-BPEL 2.0 messageExchange construct (as well as the BPEL4WS 1.1 Active Endpoints extension construct aex:messageExchange).
AeMessageExchangesDef Simple container for string values used for binding receives and replies
AeNamedDef Definition base for all named definition elements
AePartnerDef Definition for bpel partner.
AePartnerLinkDef Definition for bpel partner link.
AePartnerLinkDefKey This key identifies a single partner link in the Def layer.
AePartnerLinkDelegate Class to hold partner link related information.
AePartnerLinkOpKey This class combines a partner link and an operation into a key that can be used in maps and the like.
AePartnerLinksDef Container for partnerLinks.
AePartnersDef Container def for AePartnerDef objects.
AeProcessDef Definition for bpel process
AeScopeDef Definition for bpel scope.
AeSingleActivityParentBaseDef A base class for any def that has a single activity as its child.
AeTerminationHandlerDef Models the 'terminationHandler' bpel construct introduced in WS-BPEL 2.0.
AeVariableDef Definition for bpel Variable construct.
AeVariablesDef Models the variables element from BPEL.
 

Exception Summary
AeAmbiguousPartnerLinkException This exception is thrown when an ambiguous partner link name is used to resolve a partner link.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def Description

This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions.
